* Enable SSL/TLS on the SVRCONN channel
ALTER CHANNEL('DEV.APP.SVRCONN') CHLTYPE(SVRCONN) SSLCIPH('ANY_TLS12')

* Optional: Require client authentication on the channel
ALTER CHANNEL('DEV.APP.SVRCONN') CHLTYPE(SVRCONN) SSLCAUTH(REQUIRED)

* Optional but recommended: Define CHLAUTH rule to allow only clients with valid certs
ALTER QMGR CHLAUTH(DISABLED)

* Refresh SSL security settings
REFRESH SECURITY TYPE(SSL)
